summary: I’m usually not one to jump on drama with people’s headcanons ( Bi TJ in particular ) because it has no effect on the actual can...
body:
I’m usually not one to jump on drama with people’s headcanons ( Bi TJ in particular ) because it has no effect on the actual can itself. But, I feel like people need a reminder.

Headcanons are people’s own opinion on a particular matter and, I repeat, does not have an effect on canon. So let people do this. Let people have fun with a particular character! This isn’t just for Bi TJ, this is for the Jyrus shippers, Trans!Marty, and Lesbian!Amber. Let people enjoy stuff. People’s headcanons don’t have any effect of the canon of the show. 

Also, to clear up anything, I do not headcanon TJ as bisexual, but I do stay in my own lane and let people enjoy things. I’m not here to be the fun police.
